videos.description: Darryl Morsell finds Michal Cekovsky off the screen for a wide-open dunk.
videos.headline: Maryalnd's Morsell-Cekovsky connection leads to dunk

videos.description: Jae'Sean Tate blocks Anthony Cowan and then throws down the two-handed dunk in transition.
videos.headline: Ohio State's Tate turning defense into offense
